snippet.title: Warframe Tutorial - Dark Sectors
snippet.description:
Coming in Update 13 -- Tenno are building Solar Rails to bring back the light to the Dark Sectors throughout the Solar System.  

Ready your Clan to begin building Solar Rails and lay claim to these lost outposts on the Solar Map. Collect Tribute from everyone who uses your rail but stay alert, Tenno -- other Clans can try to overtake your Sector.

http://www.warframe.com
http://forums.warframe.com
